{"tid":511532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【孌童歪風】出現兒童意淫影片 YouTube恐成孌童交易「櫥窗」","createTime":"2017-12-27T14:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T13:26:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4391fb09ffb378aafd4550e3758a1b2ad3213072","tid":511532,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171227/large/1514377724_2926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171227%2Flarge%2F1514377724_2926.jpg&h=8fd06579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兒童色情影像向來只在不見天日的暗網橫行，但英國傳媒首次揭發連影片分享網站YouTube，也恐淪為兒童色情影像交易的「櫥窗」。不法影像提供者明目張膽地，把帶有性暗示的未成年少女片段上傳至YouTube，吸引孌童癖經加密通訊工具聯絡他們，再取得真正的兒童色情物品，YouTube更向曾瀏覽有關短片的用戶推薦同類影片。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》周三報道，一些持有兒童裸照及性侵犯兒童影片的不法分子，在YouTube開設影片頻道，專門上載露骨但內容合法的數秒短片，部份片段顯示女童正在舔舌或跳舞，另提供電郵地址，上傳者亦會在自我介紹中邀請觀眾經Telegram等加密通訊軟件接洽。記者跟部份上傳者聯絡上後，對方不諱言可交易大量兒童裸照及片段。<br />\nYouTube接獲記者舉報後才刪除有關影片，並表示片段中危害兒童的內容令人髮指，不希望內容再在YouTube出現，又稱公司有清晰指引打擊相關片段，過去數周已移除逾15萬段同類影片。<br />\n但《泰晤士報》記者在調查期間發現，瀏覽兒童意淫影片後，YouTube會向記者推薦其他同類片段。有刑事法專家指，YouTube此舉增加了觀眾接觸含孌童成份影片的機會，或構成鼓勵或協助他人收藏或展示兒童不雅照片的刑事罪行，但要有實質證據證明YouTube高層在幕後指使，才足以入罪。<br />\n《泰晤士報》上月已報道過YouTube影片含兒童色情成分，引發孌童猥褻言論，更有大企業在相關影片賣廣告。當時報道估計影片由無知兒童上傳，但為不法者所利用，今次報道則首次揭發有不法分子利用YouTube宣傳兒童色情影像。<br />\n英國內政部專責委員會去信YouTube母公司Google要求合理答覆，表示無法相信如此引起反感的片段及照片都竟然可以在YouTube出現，報道讓人質疑Google讓影像平台遠離非法內容的決心。有性罪行研究專家指，此舉令Google成為向孌童者提供兒童不雅影像的幫兇。<br />\n此外，BuzzFeed網站早前報道，有網民投訴在YouTube搜尋器打上關鍵字「如何」時，搜尋建議竟顯示出「如何與你的孩子性交」等涉及性侵犯兒童的字眼。YouTube其後表示已移除相關建議，並承諾查明原因。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171227/57633319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57633319&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d3742fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57633319&h=a34191da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171227/57633319</a>"},{"pid":"112cb54bf566796159424e79432944222cd7a689","tid":511532,"uid":113773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982e6084f48fe268a386497cd31190da560b5419","tid":511532,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fa3fdadb97d1c59f4602211407ed186fe0da09","tid":511532,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"112cb54bf566796159424e79432944222cd7a689","tid":511532,"uid":113773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"FBI"},{"pid":"66e7a411c4777567ad38037f21505718a17133a4","tid":511532,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbc88b7de4b3c8e17296930d0d4f003beda3931","tid":511532,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:13:54.00